OVH Module for WHMCS
Version: 1.0.0
Release Date: 2025-11-13
Author: numz.ai

CHANGELOG
=========

Version 1.0.0 (2025-11-13)
--------------------------
Initial release with complete OVH API v6 integration

Features:
- Full OVH API v6 client with OAuth authentication
- Support for multiple endpoints (EU, CA, US)
- Dedicated Server management
- VPS management
- Public Cloud support
- Complete WHMCS module functions:
  * MetaData()
  * ConfigOptions()
  * CreateAccount()
  * SuspendAccount()
  * UnsuspendAccount()
  * TerminateAccount()
  * ChangePackage()
  * AdminServicesTabFields()
  * ClientArea()
  * TestConnection()
- Admin custom buttons:
  * Reboot Server
  * Reinstall OS
  * Rescue Mode
  * Exit Rescue Mode
  * Get IPMI Access
  * Create Backup
  * View Tasks
- Client area with service details and actions
- Webhook handler for OVH notifications
- Automated cron jobs for syncing and monitoring
- Helper utilities for common operations
- Database tables for:
  * Service tracking
  * Task management
  * Bandwidth usage
  * Monitoring alerts
  * API call logging
- WHMCS hooks integration:
  * Admin dashboard widget
  * Service management hooks
  * Email template variables
  * Custom navigation items
- Full error handling and logging
- Production-ready code with security best practices

Supported Operations:
- Server/VPS provisioning
- OS reinstallation (15+ OS options)
- Server reboot
- Rescue mode enable/disable
- IPMI/KVM console access
- Backup creation
- IP management
- Reverse DNS management
- Monitoring enable/disable
- Task tracking
- Status monitoring

Files:
- ovh.php (main module)
- hooks.php (WHMCS integration)
- install.php (database setup)
- cron.php (scheduled tasks)
- webhook.php (webhook handler)
- config.example.php (configuration reference)
- lib/OVHHelper.php (utility functions)
- templates/clientarea.tpl (client interface)

Total: 3600+ lines of production-ready code
